name: "More Than A Story" Compact Disc (Originally Recorded by 4N1)
description:
**LIMITED QUANTITY LICENSED TO ROAD TO SURRENDER FOR RESALE

UNIT PRICE: $5.00
PACKAGING/SHIPPING (US ONLY): $2.00

4N1’s first (and only) studio release. CD includes 4 tracks, including “God Is In Control,” “How You Live (Turn Up The Music),” “New Day,” and “Everything To Me,” from whose chorus comes the EP’s title. Produced by Paul Riggins, Sunset Rising Studios (VA). Released independently in May 2008. Featuring the voices of Cori Florence, Kristen Younger, Dustin Street (who currently sings with Road To Surrender), & Kayla Farmer.

TRACK LISTING:

1. God Is In Control
2. How You Live (Turn Up The Music)
3. New Day
4. Everything To Me
